FunctionalItems.Name: Privateer License
FunctionalItems.Description: This is your official licence that proves you are a Privateer! Required to join any game.

FunctionalItems.Name: App License
FunctionalItems.Description: This is your App License. It's only owned by players who are playing from the UberStrike App.

GearItems.Name: Default Hair
GearItems.Description: This is your hair. If it's on your head then you're not wearing a hat.

GearItems.Name: Jacket of Boredom
GearItems.Description: This is the boring jacket that you started with. You should get a better one if you haven't already.

GearItems.Name: Trousers of Tedium
GearItems.Description: These trousers are exceedingly drab and should be exchanged for something more flashy as soon as possible.

GearItems.Name: Beard and Mo
GearItems.Description: It's a Beard and Mo. What did you expect?

GearItems.Name: Iron Pants of Resistance
GearItems.Description: These are the most stain resistant pants in the world. They are also made of iron.

GearItems.Name: Green Beret
GearItems.Description: Wearing this is the same as carrying a sign that says "I CAN DESTROY YOU WITH MY THOUSAND YARD STARE" that people believe.

QuickItems.Name: Spring Grenades: 3
QuickItems.Description: A pack of 3 recharging spring grenades.

QuickItems.Name: Spring Grenades: 8
QuickItems.Description: A pack of 8 recharging spring grenades.

WeaponItems.Name: Handgun
WeaponItems.Description: The original Pre-UberStrike Pistol. Shoots fast and does bonus damage on headshots.

WeaponItems.Name: Judge
WeaponItems.Description: First model of the Lawmaker Handguns. The Judge is a massive revolver that noobs have learned to fear.

WeaponItems.Name: Jury
WeaponItems.Description: Second model of the Lawmaker Handguns. The Jury has a slower rate of fire than the Judge, but packs a bigger punch with each shot.

WeaponItems.Name: Executioner
WeaponItems.Description: Third model of the Lawmaker Handguns. The Executioner is slow to fire but can down an enemy in two shots.

WeaponItems.Name: Shadow Gun
WeaponItems.Description: Solid and reliable, the Shadow Gun is experimental weaponry that originated in the Underground.

WeaponItems.Name: Battlesnake
WeaponItems.Description: The Battlesnake is fastest frying weapon around. Shoots fast enough to mow the lawn if you can find enough ammo to run it.

WeaponItems.Name: Snotgun
WeaponItems.Description: Coat your enemies in snot with this foul, phlegm-flinging device.

WeaponItems.Name: Pain Hammer
WeaponItems.Description: The Pain Hammer has a disproportionately strong knockback effect. Use it to blast your foes off ledges!

WeaponItems.Name: Thunderbuss
WeaponItems.Description: The thunderous blast that this shotgun issues can be heard miles away. Fear the Thunderbuss.

WeaponItems.Name: Vandalizer
WeaponItems.Description: The Vandalizer is the premier mess-making weapon available today.

WeaponItems.Name: Mad Splatter
WeaponItems.Description: The owners of this particular splatter gun model tend to live much longer lives than their counterparts, but they all go bonkers in the end...

WeaponItems.Name: Enamelator
WeaponItems.Description: Blast your enemies shiny with this high-damage, high-impact launcher!

WeaponItems.Name: The Final Word
WeaponItems.Description: Launches stickybombs that detonate manually with secondary fire.

WeaponItems.Name: UMG
WeaponItems.Description: The Uber Machine Gun. Upgraded version of the classic machine gun with a higher damage output.

WeaponItems.Name: SPAS-12 Black
WeaponItems.Description: Using some of the energy of each shot to cycle the action and land a new round. The Black edition benefits from additional start ammo.
